----------------------
DÁIFÁ
    Produce one random primary-Odù simulation.

TẸ IFÁ
    Perform one circular cast.

    The first use preserves the first side.
    The second use produces the second side and combines both
    into one complete Odù.

PRINTODU
    Display the latest processor result Y as a proper Odù.

PRINTODUALL
    Display Y, RA, RD, R0 and T as proper Odù forms.


